Open Netbeans
Download the lastestverson symfony
Place the ziped file unzipped in the htdocs of xammp
OPEN up netbeans
create new project 
select phpnext
pick a name and so on (install to the htdocs)
slect symfony 2 php web framework
click settings
point symfony to the zip folder
point php to php.exe in the xammp
click finish


all done


right click the main folder and press run command
click generate bundle
enter name  always finish with Bundle

